query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_keywords,
  SUM(impressions) as total_impressions,
  SUM(clicks) as total_clicks,
  SUM(spend) as total_spend,
  SUM(sales) as total_sales,
  SUM(orders) as total_orders
FROM keywords
LIMIT 1;
